{"tid":1225711,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[長輩圖]未來目標係打建制派  攻擊議席","createTime":"2019-06-15T08:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T06:17:14.000Z","uid":74954,"like":152,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"522e7fc7e0f7e6cf545f656b96adb6cb33dc517f","tid":1225711,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:20:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重要指示</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家援例   <br />\n只係令到佢地政府可以平息單野  想爭取番藍絲/中遊支持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地有更大既目標就係<span style=\"color: red;\">打散建制派</span>內部支持<br />\n進行<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">內部分化</span></span>佢地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">選舉就到</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幫大家出小小idea 方向！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最衰都係建制派無啦啦轉風，唔全力支持政府，搞到政府咁就跪倒，以後仲點有權威?<br />\n我屋企人都話以後不再選建制派</span></span>"},{"pid":"02afd5f5e99a013f7bb0fd11c419d890ea2bc8d4","tid":1225711,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:21:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c1fe81fb512ae898890ac34096a1c9487b0a2da","tid":1225711,"uid":74954,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5f2e3f7e0ea5e387054a4be62118c14acc89addb","tid":1225711,"uid":48873,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:29:09.000Z","msg":"推一推 不過未係最急切"},{"pid":"e87867b6389cb62c6545f7549ff3975aa5dcced2","tid":1225711,"uid":90883,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"推 其實好急切 守住立法會 其實好多害死香港既政策都可以避免到"},{"pid":"35747f21bf8ada087c0e2dca2d9f90c3bb94a6d1","tid":1225711,"uid":74954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:36: